|Viewers         = 0.7
|ShortSummary    = It is Mikayla's birthday and Mason's brother Jason visits, but Mason is not so welcoming due to an incident when they were children. When the kings make Jason head guard, Mason quits and drowns his sorrows in eating. But when the Tarantula people try to roast Boomer alive, Jason cowardly runs off and it is up to Brady to convince Mason and his bloated self to come back and save Boomer. When Mason arrives, he and King Brady are captured by tarantula people. Then Jason's water scooter falls on two Tarantula People, and Jason falls on the other two, saving everyone.
